  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">PILOT IMPLEMENTATION OF SCORE PROGRAMME IN TURKEY</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This new implementation targeting the H&amp;M Suppliers in Turkey will take place as an additional component to the ongoing pilot implementation of SCORE Programme in Turkey project. It will specifically target 10 supplier enterprises of H&amp;M in two different provinces in Turkey. One of the province will be Istanbul and the second province will be decided in consultancy between H&amp;M and ILO Turkey. The implementation for H&amp;M suppliers will focus on two modules of the SCORE Programme which are Module 1: Workplace Cooperation and Module 5: Safety and Health at Work: A platform for Productivity. This new component will target creation and strengthening of local capacities for SCORE implementation on Module 5: Safety and Health at Work as well as improvement of productivity of selected H&amp;M supplier enterprises through improvement of working conditions in these enterprises by the SCORE trainings and in-factory consultancies.</narrative>
  </description>
